related_questions.snippet: Staples' attempted acquisition of Office Depot is done for. ... Staples tried to negotiate, but the commission wasn't having it. This is Staples' second failed Office Depot merger. Staples announced its plan to acquire Office Depot in February of 2015, for what was valued at the time to be $6.3 billion in cash and stock.May 10, 2016

related_questions.question: Do staples still have stores?
related_questions.snippet: The US owner of Staples has sold the UK arm, which employs 1,100 people across 106 stores, to Hilco for a "nominal" sum.
